---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About me and what I do">
  <div class="space-y-12 prose max-w-none">
    <section class="pt-4">
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Hi! I'm Jaison, and I build things with code.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2>What I Do</h2>

      <p>
        I'm passionate about using technology to solve real problems. My interests span across
        artificial intelligence, cryptocurrency, automation, and building products that people love.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, I'm exploring how AI can augment human capabilities, particularly in areas like
        personal productivity, decision-making, and creative work. I also follow the crypto space
        closely, especially developments in decentralized finance and Web3 infrastructure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2>What I Write About</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li>
          <strong>Tech & AI:</strong> Practical guides, tutorials, and thoughts on emerging technology
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Crypto & Web3:</strong> Market analysis, protocol deep-dives, and decentralization
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Building in Public:</strong> Project updates, learnings, and transparent progress
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Growth:</strong> Productivity, learning strategies, and life systems
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2>Projects</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personal AI Assistant</h3>
          <p>
            Built a custom AI assistant that runs 24/7, handles scheduling, monitors news sources,
            and helps me stay organized. Uses Claude AI with custom integrations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">[Your Project Name]</h3>
          <p>
            [Description of another project you're working on or have built]
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>

      <p>
        I'm always interested in connecting with people building interesting things. Feel free to
        reach out!
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-6 text-lg">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
          Twitter
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:you@example.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
          Email
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <h2>This Site</h2>

      <p>
        This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> and <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind CSS</a>.
        It's hosted on Cloudflare Pages and deploys automatically from GitHub.
      </p>

      <p>
        The design is inspired by the clean, minimalist aesthetic of sites like
        <a href="https://www.benkuhn.net">Ben Kuhn's blog</a>,
        <a href="https://www.natebjones.com">Nate B Jones</a>, and
        <a href="https://paulstamatiou.com">Paul Stamatiou</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
